### US226 - Parts Inventory & Low-Stock Alerts

### LOGIN - run this request first
POST http://localhost:8081/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "supervisor",
  "password": "supervisor123"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("token", response.body.token);
%}

###

### US226 - Parts usage inventory
GET http://localhost:8081/api/maintenance/parts/inventory
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### US226 - Low-stock alerts with default threshold
GET http://localhost:8081/api/maintenance/parts/low-stock
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### US226 - Low-stock alerts with custom threshold
GET http://localhost:8081/api/maintenance/parts/low-stock?threshold=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
